#Claymore's Dual Ethereum + Decred/Siacoin/Lbry/Pascal/Blake2s/Keccak AMD+NVIDIA GPU Miner  
https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=1433925.0


#XMR-STAK 
XMR-Stak is a universal Stratum pool miner. This miner supports CPUs, AMD and NVIDIA gpus
 * Native algorithms which not depends on any block versions:
 *
 *    # 1MiB scratchpad memory
 *    cryptonight_lite
 *    cryptonight_lite_v7
 *    # 2MiB scratchpad memory
 *    cryptonight
 *    cryptonight_v7
 *    # 4MiB scratchpad memory
 *    cryptonight_heavy
CPU: xmrig v2.5.0+, xmr-stak v2.4.3+ with cryptonight_v7 algo
AMD GPU: xmrig-amd v2.5.0+, xmr-stak v2.4.3+ with cryptonight_v7 algo, Cast XMR Vega v0.9.0+ with --algo=1 switch
nVidia GPU: xmrig-nvidia v2.5.0+, xmr-stak v2.4.3+ with cryptonight_v7 algo
BENCHMARKS: https://www.xmrstak.com


Reference:
https://github.com/fireice-uk/xmr-stak
